snippet.title: Cartel Tycoon | Out of EA Trailer [GOG]
snippet.description:
✅ Link to the game 👉 https://bit.ly/3SlLPVw

Set in the fictionalized '80s Latin America, Cartel Tycoon tells the story of a time when cocaine took over first the US, and then the whole world. Ridiculously rich drug kingpins rule over glorious empires, creating thousands of jobs. But a maelstrom of violence threatens this criminal underworld from within.
